<!-- begin featured neighborhoods -->

<div class="container marketing">

  <div class="row-space-3">
    <div class="section-intro">
      <h2>Neighborhoods in Need</h2>
      <p>Not sure where you're most needed? See where you can lend a hand all around the world.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">

    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag "tornado.jpg", class: "img-rounded", style: "width: 250px; height: 250px;" %>
      <h2>Tuscaloosa, AL</h2>
      <p>A F5 tornado ripped though this city killed over 50 people and over 250 people across the state. Thousands were left without food or shelter. See how you can help people in this area.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->

    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag "earthquake.jpg", class: "img-rounded", style: "width: 250px; height: 250px;" %>
      <h2>Haiti</h2>
      <p>The earthquake affected the lives of everyone in Haiti. Constuction, debris removal, infrastructure, and sanitation are just a few of the dire needs for our neighbors in Haiti. See how you can lend a hand!</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->

    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag "katrina.jpg", class: "img-rounded", style: "width: 250px; height: 250px;" %>
      <h2>New Orleans, LA</h2>
      <p>Hurricane Katrina decimated much of New Orleans leaving residents with the task of rebuilding their community.  See how you can help out the locals and help them build back their proud community and get neighbors back on their feet!</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->

  </div><!-- /.row -->



</div><!-- /.container marketing -->

